       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. DEPOSIT-CALC.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 DEPOSIT-DATA.
          05 PRINCIPAL       PIC 9(9)V99 VALUE 10000.00.
          05 INTEREST-RATE   PIC V9999    VALUE .0550.
          05 TERM-YEARS      PIC 99       VALUE 05.
          05 COMPOUND-FREQ   PIC 99       VALUE 12.
          05 TOTAL-INTEREST  PIC 9(9)V99.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       CALCULATE-INTEREST.
           * Складна банківська логіка розрахунку капіталізації
           COMPUTE TOTAL-INTEREST = PRINCIPAL * ((1 + INTEREST-RATE / COMPOUND-FREQ) ** (COMPOUND-FREQ * TERM-YEARS))
           DISPLAY "FINAL BALANCE: " TOTAL-INTEREST.
           GOBACK.
